stmt:
EXPLAIN (ANALYZE, FORMAT JSON)
SELECT count(*) FROM category as category
JOIN subcategory as subcategory
ON subcategory.category_id = category.id
JOIN product as product
ON product.subcategory_id = subcategory.id
JOIN order_details as order_details
ON order_details.product_id = product.id
JOIN "order" as "order"
ON "order".id = order_details.order_id
JOIN deliverer as deliverer
ON deliverer.id = "order".deliverer_id;

JOIN "order" as "order"
ON "order".id = order_details.order_id
JOIN customer as customer
ON customer.id = "order".customer_id

ON deliverer.id = "order".deliverer_id
JOIN discount as discount
ON discount.id = "order".discount_id
JOIN product as product
ON product.id = order_details.product_id
JOIN subcategory as subcategory
ON subcategory.id = product.subcategory_id;

stmt:
EXPLAIN (ANALYZE, FORMAT JSON)
SELECT count(*) FROM category as category
JOIN subcategory as subcategory
ON subcategory.category_id = category.id
JOIN product as product
ON product.subcategory_id = subcategory.id
JOIN order_details as order_details
ON order_details.product_id = product.id
JOIN "order" as "order"
ON "order".id = order_details.order_id
JOIN customer as customer
ON customer.id = "order".customer_id
JOIN discount as discount
ON discount.id = "order".discount_id;

stmt:
EXPLAIN (ANALYZE, FORMAT JSON)
SELECT count(*) FROM category as category
JOIN subcategory as subcategory
ON subcategory.category_id = category.id
JOIN product as product
ON product.subcategory_id = subcategory.id
JOIN order_details as order_details
ON order_details.product_id = product.id
JOIN "order" as "order"
ON "order".id = order_details.order_id
JOIN customer as customer
ON customer.id = "order".customer_id
JOIN deliverer as deliverer
ON deliverer.id = "order".deliverer_id
JOIN discount as discount
ON discount.id = "order".discount_id;

stmt:
EXPLAIN (ANALYZE, FORMAT JSON)
SELECT count(*) FROM order_details as order_details
JOIN "order" as "order"
ON "order".id = order_details.order_id
JOIN deliverer as deliverer
ON deliverer.id = "order".deliverer_id
JOIN discount as discount
ON discount.id = "order".discount_id
JOIN product as product
ON product.id = order_details.product_id;
